claim.claim-text:
1. An apparatus for determining a sensor position comprising:
a plurality of discrete Fourier transform calculators operable to process input data to yield a magnitude response of the input data at each of a plurality of candidate frequencies;
a comparator operable to compare the magnitude responses to yield a winning candidate frequency;
a servo controller operable to process at least one servo field in the input data to identify a position of a sensor based on the at least one servo field; and
a servo frequency synthesizer operable to establish a frequency of operation in the servo controller based at least in part on the winning candidate frequency.
